  <div style="width:100%;max-width:720px;text-align:center;padding:36px 0 8px;">\
    <p style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:400;color:#4a5568;line-height:1.75;margin:0;">When an external situation demands a response, the hardest question is often whether to respond at all. This framework walks you through that decision layer by layer \'97 the output will tell you where you stand and what to do next.</p>\
    <p style="font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:500;color:#4a5568;line-height:1.7;margin:14px 0 0;">You don't have to have the right answers, but it's your job to ensure the right questions are being asked.</p>\
